---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import SiteFooter from "../../components/SiteFooter.astro";

const pageTitle =
  "Poulomi Florique – 3 BHK Bloomscapes® Homes on Thanisandra Main Road, North Bangalore";
const pageDescription =
  "Explore Poulomi Florique – premium 3 BHK Bloomscapes® residences on Thanisandra Main Road, North Bangalore. 9-acre IGBC-oriented community with 768 Vastu-compliant homes, 80%+ open spaces and 40+ lifestyle amenities.";

const developerName = "Poulomi Estates";
const locationLine = "Thanisandra Main Road, near Bhartiya City, North Bangalore";
const configSummary = "Premium 3 BHK (with select 2.5 BHK) residences";
const landArea = "Approx. 9 acres";
const totalUnits = "Approx. 768 apartments";
const openSpace = "80–85% open, landscaped spaces";
const amenitiesCount = "40+ amenities including 52,900 sq.ft clubhouse";
const brochureUrl = "/assets/poulomi-florique-brochure.pdf"; // upload this in /public/assets
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-4 pb-12 lg:pb-16">
    {/* Breadcrumb */}
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-4 mb-6 text-xs text-slate-400">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-cyan-300">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1.5 text-slate-600">/</span>
      <a href="/#properties" class="hover:text-cyan-300">Properties</a>
      <span class="mx-1.5 text-slate-600">/</span>
      <span class="text-slate-300">Poulomi Florique</span>
    </div>

    {/* HERO SECTION */}
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10">
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr,0.9fr] items-start">
        {/* Left: Title + narrative */}
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/40 bg-slate-900/70 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-cyan-200">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-ping-once"></span>
            Launching in North Bangalore
          </span>

          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight">
            Poulomi Florique – Life in Full Bloom on{" "}
            <span class="text-cyan-300">Thanisandra Main Road</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-200 max-w-2xl">
            Florique is a nature-forward, premium apartment community by {developerName}, 
            designed around their signature Bloomscapes® landscaping concept. 
            Spread across {landArea}, the project blends 3 BHK homes, large open podiums, 
            and over {amenitiesCount} to create a quiet, garden-like pocket 
            in rapidly growing North Bangalore.
          </p>

          <div class="grid gap-3 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200 max-w-xl">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
              <p>Vastu-compliant 3 BHK homes with privacy-led planning and sizeable unit sizes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400"></span>
              <p>Bloomscapes® floral landscapes with dedicated thematic gardens and calm outdoor pockets.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-300"></span>
              <p>Strategic location next to Bhartiya City with strong rental and long-term appreciation potential.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="#enquire"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 px-5 py-2 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 shadow-lg shadow-cyan-400/40 hover:bg-cyan-300 transition-colors"
            >
              Request a Call Back
            </a>
            <a
              href={brochureUrl}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-500/70 bg-slate-900/70 px-5 py-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-100 hover:border-cyan-300/70 hover:text-cyan-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Download Official Brochure (PDF)
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Right: Project stats card */}
        <aside class="relative">
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-2xl shadow-[0_0_45px_rgba(15,23,42,0.9)] p-5 space-y-5">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">Flagship Project</p>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-100">
                  Poulomi Florique – North Bangalore
                </p>
              </div>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-emerald-400/50 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-emerald-200">
                Bloomscapes® Living
              </span>
            </div>

            <dl class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-xs sm:text-[13px] text-slate-200">
              <div>
                <dt class="text-slate-400">Location</dt>
                <dd class="font-medium">{locationLine}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-slate-400">Configuration</dt>
                <dd class="font-medium">{configSummary}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-slate-400">Land Area</dt>
                <dd class="font-medium">{landArea}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-slate-400">Total Units</dt>
                <dd class="font-medium">{totalUnits}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-slate-400">Open Spaces</dt>
                <dd class="font-medium">{openSpace}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-slate-400">Amenities</dt>
                <dd class="font-medium">{amenitiesCount}</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>

            <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-4 text-xs text-slate-300 space-y-1.5">
              <p>
                <span class="font-semibold text-slate-100">Developer:</span> {developerName}
              </p>
              <p class="text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
                All project information is based on publicly available material and developer communication.
                Please reconfirm current details, pricing and availability at the time of enquiry.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* PROJECT SNAPSHOT */}
    <section id="overview" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-10 lg:mt-14 space-y-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Project Snapshot</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            A quick overview of what makes Florique an interesting pick for end-users and investors.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-[11px] text-slate-400">
          RERA details, current status and inventory will be updated once officially available.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-300">Configuration & Scale</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• 9-acre community with approx. 768 apartments.</li>
            <li>• Predominantly 3 BHK apartments with select 2.5 BHK options.</li>
            <li>• Vastu-compliant planning with privacy-led layouts.</li>
            <li>• Unit sizes ranging roughly from ~1585 to ~2740 sq.ft (2.5 & 3 BHK variants).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-300">Bloomscapes® & Open Spaces</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• 80–85% open, floral-themed spaces inspired by Bangalore’s garden-city legacy.</li>
            <li>• Dedicated gardens: butterfly, fragrant, herb & ginger, reflexology and leisure lawns.</li>
            <li>• Vehicle-free podium experience with walking trails and sit-out pockets.</li>
            <li>• Landscaped arrival zones, event lawns and community courtyards.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-300">Lifestyle & Wellness</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• ~52,900 sq.ft clubhouse with indoor gym, games, studios and social lounges.</li>
            <li>• Dedicated sports & wellness zone with courts, rinks and fitness corners.</li>
            <li>• Multiple pools – lap pool, kids pool, Jacuzzi-style features and aquatic decks.</li>
            <li>• Thoughtful zoning for kids, seniors, work-from-home and social gatherings.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* LOCATION & CONNECTIVITY */}
    <section id="location" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-12 lg:mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr,0.9fr] items-start">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
          Location & Connectivity – Thanisandra Main Road, North Bangalore
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-200">
          Florique sits just off Thanisandra Main Road, next to Bhartiya City – one of North Bangalore’s most
          established integrated townships. That means residents plug into a ready ecosystem of offices, schools,
          retail and hospitality, while still living inside a quieter, nature-focused enclave.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
          <li>• Immediate access to Bhartiya City IT, residential and retail ecosystem.</li>
          <li>• Good proximity to Manyata Tech Park, Karle SEZ and other key employment hubs.</li>
          <li>• Connectivity via ORR and planned/upcoming Metro corridors across North Bangalore.</li>
          <li>• Social infra including schools, hospitals and malls within a practical drive-time radius.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          Travel times and connectivity are indicative based on current infrastructure; they may improve further
          with ongoing road and metro upgrades.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* simple location highlights list */}
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/80 p-5 space-y-4">
        <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">Neighbourhood Highlights</p>
        <dl class="space-y-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
            <dt>Bhartiya Mall of Bengaluru</dt>
            <dd class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">Approx. short drive via internal township roads</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
            <dt>Manyata Tech Park</dt>
            <dd class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">Approx. 25–30 min drive, depending on traffic</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
            <dt>Elements Mall / Hebbal</dt>
            <dd class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">Approx. 20–30 min belt</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
            <dt>Kempegowda International Airport</dt>
            <dd class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">Approx. 30–40 min depending on time of day</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <dt>Schools & Healthcare</dt>
            <dd class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">
              DPS North, REVA University, Orchids, leading hospitals & clinics in the wider North Bangalore belt.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* AMENITIES & LIFESTYLE */}
    <section id="amenities" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-12 lg:mt-16 space-y-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Amenities & Everyday Lifestyle</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            Designed as a complete lifestyle campus with strong emphasis on outdoor life, sports and social spaces.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 max-w-sm">
          Exact amenity list, phasing and access rules are as per the final agreement and developer documentation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-300">Sports & Wellness</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• Full basketball court, tennis court and dedicated futsal court.</li>
            <li>• Multiple pickleball courts catering to new-age sports demand.</li>
            <li>• Roller skating rink, fitness corners and jogging / walking paths.</li>
            <li>• Large indoor gymnasium and studio spaces under the clubhouse.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-300">Water, Greens & Calm</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• 25M lap pool, kids’ pool, bubbling pools and water features.</li>
            <li>• Floral parterre, butterfly gardens and fragrant / herb gardens.</li>
            <li>• Reflexology garden and elderly-friendly seating zones.</li>
            <li>• Pet garden, sit-out decks and quiet corners for reading or work.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-300">Clubhouse & Community</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• Multi-purpose halls, party lounges and social gathering spaces.</li>
            <li>• Business lounge, co-working style corners and tuition / AV rooms.</li>
            <li>• Creche, kids’ play areas and teen hangout pockets.</li>
            <li>• Zonal planning to separate high-energy and calm-use areas.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* FLOOR PLANS & UNIT MIX */}
    <section id="plans" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-12 lg:mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr,0.95fr] items-start">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Floor Plans & Unit Mix</h2>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-200">
          Florique offers a range of 2.5 and 3 BHK layouts with generous living spaces, wide frontages and
          thoughtful storage. While exact plans should be checked in the official brochure and with the sales
          team, the broad unit mix is as below:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
          <li>• 2.5 BHK homes around ~1585 sq.ft (select towers).</li>
          <li>• 3 BHK homes in multiple variants from ~1780 sq.ft up to ~2030 sq.ft.</li>
          <li>• Larger 3 BHK + maid / study homes in the ~2200–2700+ sq.ft range.</li>
          <li>• No common walls between units as per brochure, aiding privacy and acoustic comfort.</li>
          <li>• Higher floor-to-ceiling height in living zones (as highlighted by the developer), giving an airy feel.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          For exact floor plans, stack diagrams and tower-wise availability, please refer to the official 
          Florique brochure and confirm the latest version with the developer or authorised channel partners.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Placeholder for floor-plan imagery */}
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-white/20 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center gap-3">
        <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-400">
          Floor Plans / Master Plan Visual
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200 max-w-xs">
          You can embed tower-wise floor plan images or a master plan visual here once your media library
          is finalised. For now, this acts as a placeholder, keeping the layout ready.
        </p>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-slate-600/70 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] text-slate-300">
          Suggested ratio: 16:9 or 4:3 high-resolution PNG / JPG
        </span>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* SPECIFICATIONS */}
    <section id="specifications" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-12 lg:mt-16 space-y-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Key Specifications (Highlights)</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            A quick summary of the structural and interior specification direction, as presented in the brochure.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 max-w-sm">
          For contractual specifics, always refer to the official specification sheet attached to the agreement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-300">Structure & Shell</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• RCC structural shear wall system as per relevant IS codes.</li>
            <li>• Exterior envelope finished with texture and exterior-grade paints.</li>
            <li>• Vitrified tiles for common lobbies and circulation spaces.</li>
            <li>• Basement and parking areas finished with appropriate VDF / marked flooring.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-300">Interiors & Finishes</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• Large-format vitrified tiles in living, dining, kitchen and key bedrooms.</li>
            <li>• Bathrooms with vitrified tile flooring and dado, plus grid false ceilings.</li>
            <li>• Walls with putty, primer and low-VOC emulsion paints across rooms.</li>
            <li>• UPVC windows, balcony doors and 8 ft. factory-made internal doors (as per brochure).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-300">MEP, Safety & Smart Features</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
            <li>• Gravity-based water system with treated water and individual metering.</li>
            <li>• FTTH / TV and internet provision across key rooms.</li>
            <li>• Fire detection and suppression systems as per regulations.</li>
            <li>• Digital main door locks, app-based communication and EV charging provisions in parking (as per brochure).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* INVESTMENT VIEW */}
    <section id="investment" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-12 lg:mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr,0.9fr] items-start">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
          Investment View – North Bangalore & Florique’s Positioning
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-200">
          North Bangalore has been one of the most closely watched corridors in the city, thanks to the airport,
          tech parks, large integrated townships and steady infrastructure upgrades. For serious buyers and
          investors, Florique aims to sit at the intersection of lifestyle, sustainability and long-term value.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
          <li>• Market studies indicate mid-to-premium projects in North Bangalore have seen ~5–10% annual capital appreciation in recent years.</li>
          <li>• Rental yields in quality projects near major tech hubs often hover in the ~4–5% band, especially for well-sized 3 BHK units.</li>
          <li>• Florique’s adjacency to Bhartiya City, and proximity to Manyata and other employment centres, supports both end-use and rental demand.</li>
          <li>• The Bloomscapes® concept and sustainability-forward positioning may appeal to a more discerning, long-term audience.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
          This is not investment advice. Always evaluate your own financial situation, risk profile and conduct
          independent due diligence or speak to a professional advisor before making a purchase decision.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/80 p-5 space-y-3 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
        <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">
          Who Might Florique Suit?
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li>• IT / tech professionals working in Manyata, Bhartiya or neighbouring tech belts.</li>
          <li>• Families upgrading from older 2/3 BHKs who value open spaces and curated amenities.</li>
          <li>• Investors looking at North Bangalore as a 7–10 year horizon story with relatively stable demand.</li>
          <li>• NRIs and outstation buyers seeking a master-planned, township-adjacent community.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 pt-2 border-t border-white/10">
          Brick.com acts as a channel partner, helping you compare, shortlist and visit projects like Florique with
          additional context around micro-market trends, rental demand and long-term livability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* FAQ SECTION */}
    <section id="faq" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 mt-12 lg:mt-16 space-y-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            Some of the common questions serious buyers usually ask about a project like Florique.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-200">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50 text-sm">
            Where exactly is Poulomi Florique located in North Bangalore?
          </h3>
          <p>
            Florique is planned on Thanisandra Main Road, in the North Bangalore belt, 
            near Bhartiya City and within driving distance of Manyata Tech Park and Hebbal.
            This gives it access to both township-style conveniences and wider city connectivity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50 text-sm">
            What configurations and sizes are available at Florique?
          </h3>
          <p>
            As per the current brochure, the project is largely focused on 3 BHK apartments, 
            with select 2.5 BHK layouts. Unit sizes span roughly from the mid-1500 sq.ft range 
            up to the 2700+ sq.ft bracket across different towers and variants.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50 text-sm">
            Is Poulomi Florique a good fit for pure investors, or mainly end-users?
          </h3>
          <p>
            The project is positioned as an end-user friendly, lifestyle community with a strong amenity mix and
            landscape focus. However, the North Bangalore story, adjacency to major tech hubs and township
            ecosystem also make it relevant for investors looking at rental yield and long-term appreciation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 space-y-2">
